description:
Ichigo decides to spend the weekend with Masaya helping out at the aquarium for a children`s event. On the day of the event, Ichigo is enjoying her date night while volunteering, but then Kish shows up and wants a date of his own with her.
Source: Wikipedia

titles.title: Step Up! Ichigo Koi no Second Stage!
Step Up! Ichigo`s Romance Enters the Next Stage!
Step up! いちご恋のセカンドステージ!
